lead_paragraph: Hon. THOMAS F. MARSHALL has managed to keep himself within range of the public eye, these ten or a dozen years, but it is "desperate" hard to say what sensible things he has done to de serve it. In fact he belongs to a school of politicians whose scarcity is their most agreeable feature.
